high_descs: Turn around and walk to the table.

Place the plate in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the round table.
Pick up the plate from the round table.
Turn around and move forward to the counter, then go to the fridge to your left.
Open the fridge, put the plate inside and chill it, then take the plate out.

Open the microwave, put the plate inside, and close it.
